title: RHOBH 14 Friends & 23 Rooms
itunes:title: RHOBH 14 Friends & 23 Rooms
description:
Danny recaps this week's episode of The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which saw the galls on their Mexico trip. The group splits up between surfing and shopping, tries to get to the bottom of the exhausting Crystal/Sutton stuff, and we're introduced to something in Diana's past. It's a good episode, this I promise you.
